From Gerald Olchowy Subject Re Possible Canadian WC Team In article Gary L Dare writes nlu Nelson Lu writes CENTERS Mark Messier Rangers Messier was not invited due to his nagging While the press made an issue of it and attempted to link it to the Rangers' internal political woes Mike Keenan repeated that to Messier personally during the MSG press It makes sense Messier would probably have not declined the invitation if it were made for publicity Actually Messier was invited but declined due to nagging Keenan and Messier have always gotten dumped Steve Yzerman from the last Canada Cup team even though Yzerman had endured the training camp when Messier who had missed essentially the entire camp recovering from injuries became available at the last Gerald